@startuml
title APlay Target Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "app/linux\nCLI / desktop lifecycle" as LinuxApp
component "sdk\nCPP .so / JNI / NAPI / AAR / HAR" as Sdk
component "app/android\nActivity / Service lifecycle" as AndroidApp
component "app/harmony\nHAP / DevEco entry" as HarmonyApp
component "protocol\nRTSP / HTTP / mDNS" as Protocol
component "streaming\nRAOP / mirror / HLS / timing" as Streaming
component "crypto\nAES / FairPlay / SRP / Ed25519" as Crypto
component "osal\ncodec / render / bindings" as Osal

LinuxApp --> Protocol
LinuxApp --> Streaming
LinuxApp --> Osal
AndroidApp --> Sdk
HarmonyApp --> Sdk
Sdk --> Protocol
Sdk --> Streaming
Sdk --> Osal
Protocol --> Crypto
Protocol --> Streaming
Protocol --> Osal
Streaming --> Crypto
Streaming --> Osal

note right of Protocol
BLE discovery is TODO.
mDNS/DNS-SD is first.
end note

note right of Osal
OSAL owns codec/render and native binding adapters.
UI and business lifecycle stay in app/linux, app/android, and future app/harmony.
end note

@enduml
